hopla get user-stats - get stats of a user in JSON


syntax:
    hopla get user-stats --help
    hopla get user-stats
    hopla get user-stats all
    hopla get user-stats manapoints|mana|mp
    hopla get user-stats experience|exp|xp
    hopla get user-stats gold|gp
    hopla get user-stats --jq-filter|-j {FILTER}


Example:
```bash
# get maximum mana points
hopla get user-stats -j .maxMP

# get class (e.g. wizard)
hopla get user-stats -j .class
```
